    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Training (Chakra Control)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> </p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b>  | <b>Perform DC:</b> </p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> None</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You repeatedly use the Kinobori technique to climb trees, which grants you a +1 bonus to Chakra Control checks to tap your reserves, and grants a +1 bonus to your maximum Chakra Pool and Chakra Reserves. If you did not know the Kinobori technique (p116), you learn it as part of this training.</p>\n\n\n\n",
